  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The insect within snaps its mandibles, ferocious before even seeing another entity.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be a <span class=\"name name-fuel\">fierce</span> hunter, defeating prey and rival creatures with powerful aggression.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>其中的昆虫已经在张合颚骨，尚未接触外界便已显露出凶性。<br><br>里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将成为一位<span class=\"name name-fuel\">凶猛</span>的猎手，能以强烈的攻击性制服敌对生物与猎物。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個有生命的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且準備孵化！</span><br><br>裡面的昆蟲尚未看到其他存在體，就緊緊咬住大顎，顯得十分兇猛。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下特徵：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">強悍</span>的獵手，對獵物和敵方生物有強烈的攻擊性。"
  },
